text: Marisa Cortesi (born 3 June 1970) is a Swiss equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Chur
